    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no scratches or dings, while the interior is pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. It has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage, making it a perfect choice for a discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 49000.0,
